    "text": "# April 21, 2026  \n- Preeti's first yoga class today. She came back feeling refreshed.\n- Neetish opened up about her exam stress. Feeling better that she talked.\n- Had a call from Mohan's school about the fight with Aryan. Need to meet the principal.\n- Office: submitted the project proposal. Waiting for client approval.\n- Lunch: went to Rajkumar (a popular dhaba near Vijay Nagar). Had the famous poha.\n- Browny pulled a trick today. He escaped from the house when the gate was open.\n- Found him at the neighbor's house eating их food. Naughty boy.\n- Evening: family dinner at home. Simple but peaceful.\n- Watched the kids play with Browny in the compound.\n- Bedtime stories. Mohan requested two tonight.",
